OL,6,FThere was also the botched attempt to
OL,7,Fprivatise Channel 4, dropped after
OL,8,FRishi Sunak took office.
OL,10,FOne positive move last week is that
OL,11,Fthe Media Bill made it onto the
OL,12,Fstatute book before the unexpectedly
OL,13,Fearly dissolution of parliament.
OL,15,FThis gives Ofcom new powers over
OL,16,Fstreaming services and helps guarantee
OL,17,Fthe prominence of the public service
OL,18,Fbroadcasters' streaming services.
OL,19,FThese are welcome moves which enjoyed
OL,20,Fbroad support within the industry.
