OL,6,FPolls suggest Labour is almost certain
OL,7,Fto form the government after 4th July
OL,8,Fbarring a major upset during the
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,FThere are many questions to ask.
OL,13,FIs Labour committed to the TV licence
OL,14,Fas we know it or might it look at
OL,15,Foptions such as a "household charge"
OL,16,Ffor the BBC?
OL,18,FHow well funded should the BBC be?
OL,19,FShould there be a one-off "restorative
OL,20,Frise" in the licence fee for now?
