OL,6,FShould free licences for the over 75s
OL,7,Fbe brought back?
OL,9,FAll of us who care for the BBC can see
OL,10,Fthe direct effects of cuts ` local
OL,11,Fradio and the News Channel ` and can
OL,12,Flook out for the less apparent effects
OL,13,Fof budget shortfalls such as the
OL,14,Fnumber of prominent repeats.
OL,16,FIt is also worth asking politicians
OL,17,Fwhere they stand on privatising
OL,18,FChannel 4.
