OL,6,FI have argued before that if Channel 4
OL,7,Fis to have a safe public sector
OL,8,Ffuture, it needs to be much truer to
OL,9,Fits original character ` serious-
OL,10,Fminded, serving minorities, providing
OL,11,Fa PSB alternative to the BBC.
OL,13,FThe economic arguments against C4
OL,14,Fprivatisation are articulated well by
OL,15,Fmany independent production companies
OL,16,Fbut hardly cause a ripple with viewers
OL,17,Ffaced with another schedule which
OL,18,Fappears to be a mix of the trivial,
OL,19,Fthe derivative, the familiar and the
OL,20,Fmainstream.
