OL,6,FMore Unreported World and Derry Girls
OL,7,F` less Come Dine with Me and Double
OL,8,Fthe Money.
OL,10,FStill ` despite the protestations of
OL,11,FC4 when it faced privatisation ` it is
OL,12,Fclear that the problems in the TV ad
OL,13,Fmarket leaves the business exposed and
OL,14,Frisks the parts of it which are still
OL,15,Fspecial.
OL,17,FITV 1 and Channel 5 are, of course,
OL,18,Fpurely commercial channels and they
OL,19,Frecently agreed new licences with
OL,20,FOfcom.
