OL,6,FIt is worth remembering all the big
OL,7,Fmoves towards the creation of ITV 1 as
OL,8,Fwe now know it happened under Labour.
OL,10,FMight Ofcom be given teeth to deal
OL,11,Fmore effectively with other
OL,12,Fbroadcasters though? GB News has at
OL,13,Fthe time of writing avoided sanctions
OL,14,Ffrom Ofcom for what many in the
OL,15,Findustry consider to be serious
OL,16,Fmisdemeanours.
OL,18,FDo the "local" TV stations on Freeview
OL,19,Fwhich are not locally owned and run
OL,20,Fdeserve any protected future?
