OL,6,FThese are all important issues to
OL,7,Fhighlight to candidates.
OL,9,FJust a thought.
OL,11,FIf a "household charge" replaced the
OL,12,Flicence fee, part of it could be used
OL,13,Fto ensure all households had a
OL,14,Freliable broadband connection which
OL,15,Fwas free at the point of use.
OL,17,FThat in turn could lead to a point
OL,18,Fwhere turning off Freeview might
OL,19,Factually be realistic. But it would be
OL,20,Fa huge investment and take a very long
OL,21,Ftime.
